  "bookTitle": "Secretary (Alt)",
  "bookId": 66,
  "firstAcquaintance": "Even Lui Rin has moments when she wears a swimsuit... is this for real?!",
  "personality": "With her outfit liberated, her personality is liberated too -- Lui Rin has become more passionate. To cover up her embarrassment, she adopts the attitude that as long as she's not awkward, everyone else is the one who should feel awkward.",
  "like": "None",
  "familiarData": "Summer is dangerous -- many people get carried away and do something recklessly bold. However, because of the scars on her body, Lui Rin only wears tightly covering clothes and is essentially immune to the beach.\n\nWhat if her master gets seduced by a bad woman on the beach? Worried about her master, Lui Rin was egged on by a certain succubus who was watching the drama unfold, and broke through her limits to put on a swimsuit.\nShe couldn't let her scars make everything else suffer too --\nFollowing the succubus's advice, Lui Rin decided to reveal her expanses of pale, unblemished skin. Always one to give it her all, Lui Rin chose the most combat-effective option -- a string bikini!\n\nWearing less than everyone else, Lui Rin completely captured her master's attention, ensuring the master wouldn't be tempted by bad women. But summer isn't over yet, so Lui Rin's bodyguard mission continues.\n\nMysterious female voice: \"Not my fault~ How was I supposed to know that the usually serious Lui Rin-chan would be so bold.\"\n\nSummer makes the blood run hot -- it's all summer impulse.",
